Plush Toy: Do you want to allocate funds for weed and pest control?
- Yes, manual weeding team
	Plush Toy: Hard work, but it keeps the soil healthy. This is true sustainability.
	=> set_manual
- Yes, chemical pesticides
	Plush Toy: Cheap and fast... but they hurt the soil. Nothing else can grow there afterward.
	=> set_chemical
- No, save money for more trees
	Plush Toy: Risky... Without maintenance, even the best intentions wither.
	=> set_none

