Plush Toy: You did it! These trees will live for decades.
Plush Toy: The soil is healthier, the air is cleaner... and look! Birds are coming back.
Plush Toy: In the Philippines, only 40% of planted trees survive past 5 years due to lack of maintenance. Quality > Quantity!
